----------------------------------------------------------------------
/* transport control layer */
----------------------------------------------------------------------.
| 8 byte    | 8 byte            | 8 byte            | 32 byte   | .../
+-----------+-------------------+-------------------+-----------+-----
| length    | identification0   | identification1   | md5sum    | .../
----------------------------------------------------------------------`
Notes:
1. Every client has an identification.
2. The `length', `identification0' and `identification1' are
	hexadecimal-character.
